777
00:54:29,940 --> 00:54:31,239
- Bi. - Ya?

778
00:54:31,539 --> 00:54:34,480
Kamu harus mengawasi tamu kita.

779
00:54:34,480 --> 00:54:35,739
Aku pasti akan melakukannya, Nyonya Hong.

780
00:54:38,510 --> 00:54:39,610
Anda di sini.

781
00:54:42,650 --> 00:54:43,650
Ikuti aku.

782
00:54:49,820 --> 00:54:51,090
Kamu baik-baik saja?

783
00:54:52,530 --> 00:54:53,599
Ya.

784
00:54:55,030 --> 00:54:58,969
Anda tahu tentang hubungan Jae Jin dan Se Na, bukan?

